      <title>10 月降息预期升温，欧洲债券市场上涨势头增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，欧元区政府债券的涨势加快，因又一批疲软的经济数据增强了该地区放松货币政策的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-bonds-surge-with-ecb-cut-in-october-increasingly-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息预期和中国刺激措施推动欧洲股市创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-stocks-test-new-highs-as-china-us-fuel-global-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国一系列刺激措施以及越来越多的人相信未来几个月美国和欧元区利率将进一步下降的推动，欧洲股市周五创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/european-stocks-test-new-highs-as-china-us-fuel-global-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 07:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
